title: Svetluska
description: A 100% vegetarian/vegan restaurant serving healthy food for reasonable prices. Uses healthy grains like quinoa, buckwheat, bulgur, brown rice, wholegrain pasta. Serves soups, salads, tofu and pulses dishes. Has a good selection of raw food, including cakes. Peaceful atmosphere with a Buddhist type decor and calming music. You will receive complimentary candy or a biscuit at the end of your meal.
